tags.description: Open daily from dawn til dusk, visitors can experience two pavilions, barbeque facilities and stroll along the 500-foot boardwalk.  The park has an 8-space parking lot, benches bike racks, and one of last remaining pieces of Lehigh’s original wetlands.
tags.name: Jim Fleming Ecological Park
